{"tid":1043650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與妻爭執揮刀自斷4指 狂男︰因為不能打老婆","createTime":"2019-03-02T12:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T05:05:02.000Z","uid":225846,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"78ccd7d3a2847668088dcdb90623fb3500b0adea","tid":1043650,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:12:57.000Z","msg":"好男人當然不能打老婆，但也不要傷害自己。甘肅蘭州一名男子周五（1日）與妻子因瑣事，在家中發生爭執；男子盛怒之下，想到不能打妻子，便回身拿起一把菜刀，朝自己左手剁下去，令其左手4隻手指完全被斬斷。其妻子嚇得大驚失色，連忙把男子送到醫院治療。 <br />\n<br />\n事後，該男子及其妻子都大感後悔，認為不值為瑣事如此衝動。幸男子被送醫及時，醫生成功接駁其4根手指，惟醫生直言，男子的左手即使康復後，亦會出現功能性障礙。目前，該男子仍在醫院治療。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a911165b7f7455787203cbef5ad140038e9f89d","tid":1043650,"uid":198583,"like":4,"dislike":16,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:13:54.000Z","msg":"女人吾可以對佢太好🤦🏻&zwj;♀️"},{"pid":"8f3fe53f4d4ad2d8021feb16e2f8bc1bf1808751","tid":1043650,"uid":57185,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"笑到噴咗粒珍珠"},{"pid":"ecc358076765b98b8c1aedfc7f649ccd2a21a12e","tid":1043650,"uid":120135,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"功能性障礙"},{"pid":"692c3a829b1b4150275d97971ff8d866dbdc0b89","tid":1043650,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f3fe53f4d4ad2d8021feb16e2f8bc1bf1808751","tid":1043650,"uid":57185,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"笑到噴咗粒珍珠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:22:25.000Z","msg":"呢個仲好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd6b2e1efb6fe2e2b20c6f681db028c1b11b650","tid":1043650,"uid":228296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:22:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89223d7ebbf26394409346a652e92c38e9a017f5","tid":1